# Code owners for the-dreaming-repo.
#
# This file gates GitHub Actions workflows and CI configuration. The
# rationale (cage-match on PR #24, 2026-05-02): the workflow lint
# (lint-workflows.yml) catches PR-controlled config rewrites by reading
# the base branch's `.github/zizmor.yml`, but it cannot defend against a
# PR that rewrites the lint workflow itself. Requiring a code owner
# review on any change under `.github/` closes that bypass at the
# review-process layer.
#
# Scope is deliberately narrow — only `.github/`. Robin and other
# contributors can still PR into the rest of the repo without owner
# approval. Source files, journal content, dreams, etc. are not gated.

.github/ @nickmeinhold
